      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "ELMo was a pivotal step: it proved that deep pretrained language model representations transfer to a wide variety of NLP tasks as features. BERT (2018) pushed further by replacing LSTMs with Transformers and adopting fine-tuning rather than feature extraction as the dominant paradigm."
          }
        ]
